three of her husbands.

00:17.092 --> 00:19.263
It hurts so much.

00:19.265 --> 00:21.402
I thought I was going to die.

00:21.404 --> 00:23.944
It absolutely terrified me.

00:23.946 --> 00:25.412
And it's almost like a butchering.

00:25.414 --> 00:27.120
In the name of Jesus, you go.

00:27.122 --> 00:29.127
Vicious.

00:29.129 --> 00:32.329
They're burning them alive.

00:32.331 --> 00:35.007
Something bad's going to happen.

00:35.009 --> 00:37.916
My name is Amy Allan.

00:37.918 --> 00:39.283
There's panic.

00:39.285 --> 00:40.720
And it's almost like a butchering.

00:40.722 --> 00:41.790
I see dead people.

00:41.792 --> 00:43.928
They all died horribly.

00:43.930 --> 00:45.634
I speak to dead people.

00:45.636 --> 00:47.040
Get out of here.

00:47.042 --> 00:48.674
And they speak to me.

00:48.676 --> 00:50.713
Vicious.

00:50.715 --> 00:53.863
But there's only one way to
know if my findings are real.

00:53.865 --> 00:55.569
It doesn't matter where you are.
I'll find you.

00:55.571 --> 00:57.146
I rely on my partner.

00:57.148 --> 00:58.782
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

00:58.784 --> 01:00.685
I'm a retired New York
City homicide detective.

01:00.687 --> 01:02.389
This guy's a real piece of work.

01:02.391 --> 01:06.061
And I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:06.063 --> 01:07.563
I feel like I live in a house of Hell.

01:07.565 --> 01:08.733
It's my job to reveal them.

01:08.735 --> 01:11.005
This is not good.

01:11.007 --> 01:12.744
But Steve and I never speak...

01:12.746 --> 01:14.780
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:14.782 --> 01:16.549
Until the very end.

01:16.551 --> 01:18.022
I want my life back.

01:18.024 --> 01:20.427
When we uncover if it's
safe for you to stay...

01:20.429 --> 01:22.031
Is he trying to kill her?

01:22.033 --> 01:23.301
Or time to get out.

01:23.303 --> 01:24.974
Oh, my god.

