16:27.024 --> 16:28.189
She was.

16:28.191 --> 16:30.625
This is the 1700s.

16:30.627 --> 16:31.762
I mean, this had to be some woman

16:31.764 --> 16:33.329
to take care of a plantation this big.

16:33.331 --> 16:34.396
Mm-hmm.

16:34.398 --> 16:35.932
You can see how some of the stories

16:35.934 --> 16:38.036
might have come about her
