16:38.038 --> 16:40.405
you know, and an important person.

16:40.407 --> 16:42.505
Is it possible she's buried here, Rosa?

16:42.507 --> 16:44.007
No. That's not possible.

16:44.009 --> 16:45.109
Why is that?

16:45.111 --> 16:46.581
Because we know where she was buried.

16:46.583 --> 16:47.683
We have record.

16:47.685 --> 16:49.518
She's buried in St. James' Parish,

16:49.520 --> 16:51.152
which isn't too far from here.

16:51.154 --> 16:53.521
Okay,
