30:41.977 --> 30:44.211
And they'll hear things downstairs.

30:44.213 --> 30:46.313
There's a lot of activity,
a lot of movement,

30:46.315 --> 30:48.615
and all of that without people really here.

30:48.617 --> 30:49.650
Mm-hmm.

30:49.652 --> 30:50.984
Yeah, that's how he operates.

30:54.056 --> 30:56.590
So, what else did you see?

30:56.592 --> 30:59.259
There were two women that
