30:59.261 --> 31:04.064
The first one was extremely old,
very, very wealthy.

31:04.066 --> 31:07.701
She is from probably 1600s, 1700s.

31:07.703 --> 31:10.921
She was someone who was a decision-maker

31:10.923 --> 31:12.973
and could implement power,

31:12.975 --> 31:16.710
and from my knowledge,
as a woman at <i> that</i> time,

31:16.712 --> 31:18.345
that didn't happen.

31:18.347 --> 31:20.914
She was in control.

31:20.916 --> 31:23.550
Now, you've heard stories for years,
right, Mrs. Rollins,

31:23.552 --> 31:25.686
about people seeing an
apparition of a woman.

31:25.688 --> 31:26.720
Yes.

31:27.723 --> 31:29.990
Michael, you had told me your
daughter saw an apparition.

31:29.992 --> 31:31.358
Was it upstairs?

31:31.360 --> 31:33.894
Yeah, upstairs in the far bedroom,
in the far corner.

31:33.896 --> 31:35.696
Which would be?

31:35.698 --> 31:37.064
- Annie's room.
- Right.

31:37.066 --> 31:39.700
Now's probably a good time to tell Amy

31:39.702 --> 31:42.669
about the legend of Annie Palmer

